overview:
Invictus Marketing is a provider of internet marketing services in the Napa Valley and greater Bay Area region.

Invictus Marketing technically started in 2010 however its core services and staff existed through a previous company name, Protype Media. Under Protype Media, the main company focus was high end custom web design and development within the automotive vertical. However, as Protype Mediaâ€™s client base grew and expanded into various other verticals ranging from manufacturing, to sports, and home design, the company soon felt the need to rebrand and expand its service offerings. Protype Mediaâ€™s client base at the time was demanding a vast array of services besides web design and development which ranged from local marketing, PPC, and email marketing.

Thus under the same management team and ownership structure, a new company by the name of Invictus Marketing was born in 2010 which is dedicated to serving the ownerâ€™s home region of the Napa Valley. The company has a great desire to expand its client base to the Wine industry and between 2010 and 2012, they will be aggressively seeking clients in the Napa and Sonoma regions.

While the company does offer many internet marketing services, their specialty is helping local businesses with local search marketing.
